{"tid":2109301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明日大嶼提前周五申撥款","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T06:00:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0a5261e51bd8abc42bf68343b02cf9a09e672a","tid":2109301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/WYHWE3FC4COWMQPFK2UHDAKY2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FWYHWE3FC4COWMQPFK2UHDAKY2E%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=b146151b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FWYHWE3FC4COWMQPFK2UHDAKY2E%2F&h=56f9cfc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/WYHWE3FC4COWMQPFK2UHDAKY2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼提前周五申撥款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jOwj3eEinaBdrwxGhQMTW_hqAeo=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHRHIMQMPN3CLWMSGZKE3KZX6E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjOwj3eEinaBdrwxGhQMTW_hqAeo%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHRHIMQMPN3CLWMSGZKE3KZX6E.gif&h=d7b8db30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「明日大嶼計劃」撥款申請將提前在周五的財委會中審議。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被批倒錢落海的「明日大嶼計劃」，當。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。當局突然將撥款審議列在7月17日（周五）的財委會議程上，即本屆立法年度最後一次的會議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團體斥罔顧民情<br />\n<br />\n「守護大嶼聯盟」擔心在今屆保皇黨保駕護航下，不排除政府將硬闖關，務求今屆通過撥款。聯盟又批評，港人現正處於水深火熱的抗疫階段，加上政府強推港版國安法下，經濟前景未明，民生社會恢復極需資源，但政府強推萬億工程，儼如倒錢落海，罔顧民情，要求當局撤回計劃。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平日前亦在社交平台發文指，。。。。。。。。。。綠色和平已發起聯署，促請當局放棄明日大嶼計劃，至今已有逾9萬人簽署。"},{"pid":"25c8aad8ada3c0874ab1acb6a5b971f35a47d74f","tid":2109301,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4a2f6e2a2f703d42ca5e365ff13322ae4bf6792","tid":2109301,"uid":276273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"國家等錢使，唔整色整水，點將D錢比中資機構，然後北上呢"},{"pid":"7faf1eb167f9a6932939edccb2668be268662190","tid":2109301,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba85334f88cbfb26447f804253d69b06272cf3da","tid":2109301,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a16dc7032a8c39c24d9eaf1e12d2055b6c745f2","tid":2109301,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"Civil 仔 fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b1a65892af666ebc228b0c91f6f68454c660d9","tid":2109301,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f2946537c0c0e62dd4894f682856bf2161d67d5","tid":2109301,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"屌你咩又借工程送比支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa66efe5e6af08ae6cddedbbc70888fc8c1aa73","tid":2109301,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"730669ea840ad7db7be08a461dbad5c9e30de77e","tid":2109301,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"財散人安樂"},{"pid":"0c56ff2595377a8d17bbd3f91aeae3e106bbd234","tid":2109301,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike"